The paper discusses the use of texture-based classification techniques for plant leaf classification, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of machine learning algorithms for classification, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
